testcase.name: convert should create a single record field set from an output model with 1 single-item data model
convert should create a single record field set with all fields from an output model with 1 single-item data model
convert should create a two record field sets with all fields from an output model with 1 single-item data model and two species fields
convert should create a record field set with multiple fields for each item in an output model with a 'list' data model

convert should add all single-item dataModel values to each record field set in an output model with a 'list' data model
convert should populate the record field set with the related object ids
convert should override fields which appear in multiple components
